description:
Taking a break from VRChat content to show you the most advanced Social VR game in the world: Resonite! People build any and everything real-time while in VR together. Resonite sponsored me to showcase their creator competition winners… but this showcase turned into something WAY bigger. Please enjoy this video & give Resonite a shot!
